# Disc images and large user data - never commit copyrighted/user media
*.iso
*.cue
*.gdi
*.chd
*.cso
*.pbp
*.rvz
*.wua
*.bin
*.img
*.mdf
*.nrg
*.zip
*.rar
*.7z
!MAME_GPL-2.0.txt
!MAME_COPYING.txt

# P0 repo hygiene: this is a C# WPF project; reject Visual Basic sources and
# stray editor/sed leftovers. *.user, *.tmp, *.bak are already declared above
# and intentionally not duplicated here.
*.vb
sed*
*.lnk
*.sqlite
*.sqlite-shm
*.sqlite-wal
RedumpDB.sqlite
_backups/

*.dat
# XML is intentionally NOT globally ignored — App.config, NuGet config.xml,
# resource manifests, and ResX-adjacent files are legitimate XML in this repo.
# Only block XML that ships inside Redump / Datfiles import folders.
Redump/**/*.xml
redump/**/*.xml
Datfiles/**/*.xml
datfiles/**/*.xml
*.sbi
*.lsd
*.key
*.dkey
*.keys

# Legal release safety (from LEGAL.md §6 — entries added on top of the
# existing rules above; deliberate duplicates inside this block are harmless
# to git and kept here for documentation continuity with LEGAL.md).
*.rom
*.raw
_release/
*.bak_*
*~
**/_backups/

# Downloaded verification databases / cuesheets / keys / subchannels must
# never be committed, even if a user creates these folders by name.
Redump/
redump/
Datfiles/
datfiles/
DiscKeys/
disc-keys/
Subchannels/
subchannels/

# Independent migration work - keep out of the WPF source repository
docs/SOURCE_CLEAN_AUDIT.md

# Signing/licensing private material must never be committed
*.pfx
*.p12
*.pem
*.cer
*.crt
*.private.json
premium-license.json
premium-license.txt
license-private*
private-key*
